formers Model#5. Workflow#{6}":[90,90],"#Train a sentence-transformers Model#5. Workflow#{7}":[91,92],"#Train a sentence-transformers Model#Prerequisites":[93,102],"#Train a sentence-transformers Model#Prerequisites#{1}":[95,102]},"outlinks":[],"metadata":{"name":"train-sentence-transformers","description":"Train or fine-tune sentence-transformers models across `SentenceTransformer` (bi-encoder; dense or static embedding model; for retrieval, similarity, clustering, classification, paraphrase mining, dedup, multimodal), `CrossEncoder` (reranker; pair scoring for two-stage retrieval / pair classification), and `SparseEncoder` (SPLADE, sparse embedding model; for learned-sparse retrieval). Covers loss selection, hard-negative mining, evaluators, distillation, LoRA, Matryoshka, and Hugging Face Hub publishing. Use for any sentence-transformers training task."},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[[95,99]],"key":"00_System/Links/Gemini_Extensions/huggingface-skills/skills/train-sentence-transformers/SKILL.md"},
